OL,5,Cunrealistic
OL,7,FThe IMF brands Hunt's spending plans
OL,8,F'unrealistic', as ITV News Economics
OL,9,FEditor Joel Hills explains
OL,11,FCountries don't usually go bust, they
OL,12,Fget bailed out.
OL,14,FAnd when it comes to resources, reach
OL,15,Fand authority, the International
OL,16,FMonetary Fund () is the organisation
OL,17,Fthat acts as global lender of last
OL,18,Fresort.
OL,20,FThe IMF's job is to disperse emergency
OL,21,Floans to nations in financial distress.
