OL,7,FIt also attempts to prevent
OL,8,Fgovernments from getting into trouble
OL,9,Fin the first place but its advice
OL,10,Fisn't always welcome.
OL,12,FThe latest installment of the IMF's
OL,13,FWorld Economic Outlook - its
OL,14,Fassessment of the prospects for the
OL,15,Fworld economy - will not be going down
OL,16,Fwell in Downing Street.
OL,18,FThe IMF has downgraded its forecast
OL,19,Ffor economic growth in the UK next
OL,20,Fyear and cautions Rishi Sunak's
OL,21,Fgovernment against tax cuts.
