OL,7,FIndeed, the IMF suggests there's a
OL,8,Fstrong case for putting taxes up,
OL,9,Fgiven that, it believes the pressures
OL,10,Fon the public finances in Britain will
OL,11,Fonly increase in the years ahead.
OL,13,FIMF advises against further tax cuts
OL,14,Fafter downgrading its forecast for
OL,15,Feconomic growth in the UK
