OL,3,CUK needs tax rises not cuts as IMF
OL,4,Cbrands Hunt's spending plans
OL,5,Cunrealistic
OL,7,FAn IMF spokesperson said: "Preserving
OL,8,Fhigh-quality public services and
OL,9,Fundertaking critical public
OL,10,Finvestments to boost growth and
OL,11,Fachieve the net zero targets, will
OL,12,Fimply higher spending needs over the
OL,13,Fmedium term than are currently
OL,14,Freflected in the government's budget
OL,15,Fplans.
OL,17,F"Accommodating these needs, while
OL,18,Fassuredly stabilising the debt/GDP
OL,19,Fratio, will already require generating
OL,20,Fadditional high-quality fiscal
OL,21,Fsavings, including on the tax side."
