OL,3,CUK needs tax rises not cuts as IMF
OL,4,Cbrands Hunt's spending plans
OL,5,Cunrealistic
OL,7,FThe statement goes on to suggest that
OL,8,Fhiking property or wealth taxes in the
OL,9,FUK and/or ditching the triple lock on
OL,10,Fpensions might be a good idea before
OL,11,Fadding: "It is in this context that
OL,12,Fstaff advises against further tax
OL,13,Fcuts".
OL,15,FThe IMF's language may seem alien and
OL,16,Fmysterious but it reads, in economist-
OL,17,Fspeak, as an authoritative challenge
OL,18,Fto the government's economic strategy.
OL,19,FThe timing - five weeks away from the
OL,20,FBudget - is incredibly inconvenient
OL,21,Ffor the chancellor.
