OL,5,Cunrealistic
OL,7,FEarlier this month and that doing so
OL,8,Fwould revive our economic prospects.
OL,10,F'If I can, I would like to reduce the
OL,11,Ftax burden,' the chancellor said
OL,13,F"I look at the numbers around the
OL,14,Fworld," Mr Hunt said. "And I see that
OL,15,Fplaces like America and countries in
OL,16,FAsia that have lower taxes have more
OL,17,Fdynamic economies and grow faster. And
OL,18,Fthat's what I would like us to be."
