OL,7,FIt would be wrong to suggest the IMF's
OL,8,Fintervention brought Liz Truss down
OL,9,Fbut it did contribute to the erosion
OL,10,Fof her credibility.
OL,12,FMr Hunt has been under pressure to cut
OL,13,Ftaxes from MPs within his party for
OL,14,Fsome time and the temptation to do so
OL,15,Fin an election year will be strong -
OL,16,Fnot least as the latest opinion polls
OL,17,Fsuggest the Conservatives face the
OL,18,Fprospect of an emphatic defeat.
