OL,3,CUK needs tax rises not cuts as IMF
OL,4,Cbrands Hunt's spending plans
OL,5,Cunrealistic
OL,7,FSince 2020, the government has spent
OL,8,Fbillions of pounds supporting British
OL,9,Fhouseholds and businesses through both
OL,10,Fthe lockdown imposed during the
OL,11,Fpandemic and the wave of inflation
OL,12,Ftriggered by Russia's invasion of
OL,13,FUkraine. It has done so using borrowed
OL,14,Fmoney.
OL,16,FThe nation's stock of debt is rising,
OL,17,Fthe cost of servicing it has increased
OL,18,F(in line with inflation and interest
OL,19,Frates) and the outlook for economic
OL,20,Fgrowth (and with it tax revenues) is
OL,21,Fweak.
