OL,7,FNevertheless, the chancellor reduced
OL,8,Fthe main rate of national insurance by
OL,9,F2 percentage points in January and has
OL,10,Fsignalled there's more to come.
OL,12,FIn recent months, the headline rate of
OL,13,Finflation has faded and markets have
OL,14,Fbegun to bet that the Bank of England
OL,15,Fwill soon think about cutting interest
OL,16,Frates.
