OL,4,Cbrands Hunt's spending plans
OL,5,Cunrealistic
OL,7,FIn theory, Mr Hunt's self-imposed
OL,8,F"borrowing rules" (which include a
OL,9,Ftarget of cutting debt as a share of
OL,10,FGDP in five years' time) mean that
OL,11,Fthere is some scope for giveaways in
OL,12,Fhis Budget.
OL,14,FBut the Institute for Fiscal Studies
OL,15,F(IFS) warns that any taxes cuts ahead
OL,16,Fof a general election are likely to
OL,17,Fprove temporary, not least because the
OL,18,Fgovernment's current spending plans
OL,19,Fare, in its view, unrealistic.
