OL,3,CUK needs tax rises not cuts as IMF
OL,4,Cbrands Hunt's spending plans
OL,5,Cunrealistic
OL,7,F"January's tax cuts were essentially
OL,8,Fpaid for by a squeeze on future public
OL,9,Fservice spending plans which might not
OL,10,Fbe delivered," says Carl Emerson of
OL,11,Fthe IFS, in response to the IMF's
OL,12,Fcomments.
OL,14,F"And government debt is forecast to
OL,15,Fremain elevated for the next few
OL,16,Fyears. The economic case for further
OL,17,Ftax cuts prior to a detailed spending
OL,18,Freview is therefore weak to say the
OL,19,Fleast."
